{"title":"月亮诗人——致一位台湾诗人","authors":["梁平"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":3,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"月亮诗人——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"致一位台湾诗人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梁平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月亮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自大洋彼岸摇渡而来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把你的喜悦你的不安你的优美思念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"停泊于月之故乡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赭色桔园和泥色的大江"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"很感性地忆起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的名字在水里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在天上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乡情诱人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最是低头亦见抬头亦望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总有满月高悬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一樽美酒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饮醉沉沉之夜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沾巾的岂止儿女愁肠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任少女演唱你心之流泉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜半银铃叮当"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山是睡了水是睡了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只月亮在床前分外明亮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"微风依然"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有洞箫点点滴滴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一曲终了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一曲又唱……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}